+a_{3}\sqrt{\frac{2}{a}}\exp\left(\frac{-i9\pi^{2}\hbar t}{2ma^{2}}\right)\sin\left(\frac{3\pi}{a}x\right)+a_{4}\sqrt{\frac{2}{a}}\exp\left(\frac{-i16\pi^{2}\hbar t}{2ma^{2}}\right)\sin\left(\frac{4\pi}{a}x\right)\text{.}
